	* makefile.dj2: stdfn.o missing in OBJ3. Reported by William D Kirby
	<wdkirby@ix.netcom.com>. demo\binary? target fixed as per suggestion
	by Juergen Breitlow <Juergen.Breitlow@blns.siemens.de> and W. Kirby.

